--- Diagnosis ---
The cluster is the correct image: the catalog offers EXACTLY the SIA-D39/E-49 pins
(postgis 3.6.3, btree_gist 1.7, pg_trgm 1.6). The ONLY blocker is that the connecting role
SPATIAL_PGUSER=`application` lacks privilege to CREATE EXTENSION. No migration, architecture,
or version problem. Awaiting operator decision on credentials/privilege before re-running Step 1.

